This guide will walk you through the process of partitioning a disk into three partitions using Disk Management in Windows. This procedure works for any internal or external hard drive that has unallocated space or is unformatted.

**Steps to Partition a Disk into 3 Partitions in Windows**

- Open Disk Management

- Select the Disk to Partition

- Create the First Partition

